#

Refreshing Homemade Lemonade

10 min
$2.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

BeverageSummer DrinkNon-Alcoholic

Description

A brisk and tangy drink to quench your thirst, perfect for any occasion.

Ingredients

  • fresh lemons: 1 cup (about 4-6 lemons)
  • granulated sugar: 1 cup
  • water: 4 cups
  • ice cubes: as needed
  • fresh mint (optional): for garnish
